Starscream wandered endlessly around the Pred cave. The bot he liked 
had pledged to another. He had come to late. He shouted out loud to 
himself.

"Even if KitKat won't love me, We can still be friends. And those 
Maximals hurt her. And they will pay. They will pay!!!!!!!"

Just than Starscream noticed that Goldeneye was close to him. A look 
of shock and panic came over his face.

"Uh...sorry about that. You'll forget what you heard, right?"

again, G'night all!)
